Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.82,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}总是寻找着看不见的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.20,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}不知它近在身旁
