Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:43.91,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}此刻依然无限光芒照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:47.42,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}星空闪烁的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:51.45,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}不计其数的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:57.78,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}如今依然等待着你去实现
