Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.68,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:33.89,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:47.52,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}轻飘飘地随风飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:51.70,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}飒爽而来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:55.52,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}若只想消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:59.42,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}就给我认真点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.32,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}黑白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:07.12,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你应该也早已厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:10.98,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}被弄脏也不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:17.48,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧拥着唯一的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:19.42,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}梦想不会就此终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:21.12,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}你依然保持本色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:25.31,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}随时都可以重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:29.93,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}摄人心魄的疯狂刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:33.10,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}才能拯救爱 woo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.24,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.86,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}谁也无法破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:41.23,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}给人添麻烦又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:43.04,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}想要继续呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:45.43,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.56,0:23:48.68,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:53.55,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「想要的只是时代的一页」
