Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是球拍？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这球拍 是上周过生日时学长送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让他教我网球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 进展顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还停留在隔着玻璃吻着玩的阶段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是隔着玻璃的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会在这种地方留下吻痕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们已经把能做的都做了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.59,0:01:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长问我下周日要不要去他家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去…去他家？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 说是想把我介绍给他父母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这是当天去男朋友家后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双亲突然有急事出门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实质上是两人独处的模式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡边同学不是结婚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丈夫又不是男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要有男朋友才是学园生活嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以抱歉了 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周日 没法跟和子去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们约过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 忘了自己的生日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有男朋友的午休啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃啊 哈密瓜包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次请你吃更好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周日空出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来须方家庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那么 要开始做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手作蛋糕是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱倒是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主角就坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男士穿围裙的样子也很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中时有交往的女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没交往过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有喜欢的人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有不少女孩子为你流泪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洋葱给辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 第一次看到须方君哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找浩史借的数码相机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这种地方派上了用场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍下了贵重的一张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身为食客 还真大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炒洋葱还太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该先炒胡萝卜之类难熟的才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么整个放进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是让无辜人士流泪的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把洋葱整个扔进锅的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就已经有罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(424,470)}你这个人还挺感情用事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)}就算不是生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人一起过周日感觉就像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望是梦的话就不要醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都第四碗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怀表是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火灾把房间都烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的礼物就用这凑合一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人 好像是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是很重要的怀表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望和子以后能留着它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没送过礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这份心就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…你几时拿走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是须方为了保护和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小一直带在身上的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是须方的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧怀表和危险的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是差劲的礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是最棒的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 上街玩去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:19.27,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}柔和阳光下 绽开的蓓蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:26.59,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小睡之中 感受着喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:34.18,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}任何人 一定都会面带微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:41.62,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将它和过去的自己重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:48.80,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}触到了觉醒的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:55.05,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好似初始的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.84,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心逐渐融化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.46,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在季节中等待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:07.11,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大地上浮现出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:10.86,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}树叶间撒落的光影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:14.39,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遍地的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:18.11,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是升空的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:21.56,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}数亿的生息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:28.60,INCN4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}此刻 世界转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24\b0}（这是让无辜人士流泪的报应 洋葱）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24\b0}（抱歉哦 抱歉）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小煌 你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合南方阳光的三人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜品要点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 今天想要刺激点的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是几位点的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要问女孩子这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窗华也可以一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透过这针孔看着就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 要和我牵手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 透视能力好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 还是活力少年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我选小酷哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Qophlite（针孔）第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,针之穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不再唱歌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没在卡拉ok唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然想起以前一起唱歌的往事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会跟任何人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的帮我保密了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小煌？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小煌的第一阶段真有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第一次转移到男孩身上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 是男孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺也去趟厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也好可爱啊 丹治惠都同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不讨厌我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和外表一样正经？班长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君绝对不会在这种时候做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第一阶段的陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是绮罗星十字团的驭星者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也对须方君做了同样的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停止这无聊的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们俩还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这身体是真正的津名志拓人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能下得了手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你还要继续玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重要的朋友拓人君的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就当场…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女孩 是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要装成别人真不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小煌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在得到了Tauburn的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过用这种方式掌握男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来素体的游戏不正面进攻就没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人的气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在楼顶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩都没事吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无孔不入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为这次中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然占据身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得能三人一起过我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗星十字团最讨厌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃蛋糕换换心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 好不烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗星十字团
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵介公子 一刀两断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Qophlight（针孔）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近几次登场镜头被她们独占
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星剑 猫眼石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星剑 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星剑 蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先前失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过男孩子的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是段难得的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体被擅自摆布 生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搅了和子的生日！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华丽的登场只是噱头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河之光啊 集于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪耀流星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 用你的针贯穿他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贯穿Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我是蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能躲过我的蛰刺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗时 高处的一方有压倒性优势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致命的一刺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能搞定的这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着能搞定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百褶喷射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tauburn…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 咬住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河之光啊 集于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪耀流星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tau飞弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒～Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人激动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,津名志拓人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超乎想象的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让窗华兴奋到这种程度的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不能陪你 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心意领了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去学长家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的被介绍给父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待落空？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那倒没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明学长看重我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里甜甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 有男朋友才算是校园生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 和子决定哪个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 看来想好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我寄人篱下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扫自不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到的令人震惊的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及被提及的 替身的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画中彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的银河已然闪耀
